ing: 3/4 pound boneless beef top round steak, 3/4 inches thick
1 (10.75 ounce) can Campbell'sÂ® Healthy RequestÂ® Condensed Cream of Mushroom Soup
des: "Streamlined in method but not in taste, SwansonÂ® Beef Broth gives this sauteed beef and mushroom recipe full hearty flavor -- plus the noodles cook right in the broth!"
ins:
Slice beef into very thin strips.
Cook beef in nonstick skillet until browned, stirring often. Remove beef.
Add soup, broth, water and onion. Heat to a boil. Stir in noodles. Cook over low heat 10 minutes or until noodles are done, stirring often. Stir in yogurt. Return beef to skillet and heat through. Garnish with parsley.
